Method		URL						Action
GET			/api/hotels				Get all/multiple hotels
POST		/api/hotels				Create a new hotel
GET 		/api/hotels/x			Get a specific hotel
PUT			/api/hotels/x			Update a specific hotel
DELETE		/api/hotels/x			Delete specifuc hotel

GET 		/api/hotels/x/reviews	Get all reviews for hotel
POST		/api/hotels/x/reviews	Get review for hotel
GET			/api/hotels/x/reviews/x'
PUT			/api/hotels/x/reviews/x'
DELETE 		/api/hotels/x/reviews/x'